  "plot outline": "The unluckiest man in Vegas - a guy whose bad luck is contagious - is used by the last of the old time mob run casinos to kill high rollers' action. That is, until he falls in love with a cocktail waitress and gets \"lady luck,\" which throws the situation into reverse. Things turn nasty when the casino director tries to break up the romance.",
